{"tid":225928,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[日本]日本公司推出穿戴式座椅","createTime":"2017-05-02T07:13:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T08:21:09.000Z","uid":64858,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d22c8ef27adc000d2b3a0abc24c84f6930d6f203","tid":225928,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:13:38.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"http://techstart.presslogic.com/2017/05/02/article/24758/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2F2017%2F05%2F02%2Farticle%2F24758%2F&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETQEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=c5a1d1e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://techstart.presslogic.com/2017/05/02/article/24758/</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n【唔怕長企】日本公司推出穿戴式座椅，減輕醫護人員長站負擔<br />\n大部份醫護人員都需要長時間站立，容易有靜脈曲張或關節炎等問題，因此有日本公司設計了穿戴式座椅 Archelis，希望能夠減輕他們的負擔。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4OTxT2o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4OTxT2o.jpg&h=bf56955d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nArchelis 座椅能夠綁在雙腿，固定大腿至腳部位置，讓醫護人員可以半蹲姿勢坐下。座椅配有兩條支架，小腿及大腿位置設低碳合金外殼，能夠支撐身體重量，讓醫護人員可以專注進行手術。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jfOE940.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjfOE940.jpg&h=225c1294&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實除了醫護人員，還有其他工種需要職員長時間站立，例如售貨員以及餐廳員工等，相信這款穿戴式座椅的設計，除了適用於醫療市場，還適用於其他行業。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：Digital Trends、Archelis<br />\n<br />\n以後大家坐港鐵唔洗再爭位,直接買呢舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e179b31cb3b06375c6cd15ad56a7553756dcebcc","tid":225928,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:19:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c053d3837e3a3c2fba51bb0960bd219cb37c35e7","tid":225928,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:38:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>20萬美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf96da49679c40a0a1059065c2bc048e80b55dc","tid":225928,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:43:07.000Z","msg":"聯合航空既恩物<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458cfe2c2e0c05c84085712b3fe067c7424f00d2","tid":225928,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T08:21:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聯合航空既恩物<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n國泰好快就改晒D位<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}